\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But at the core of what happens in our lives it really comes down to consistency or fanatical discipline!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Successful people do consistently what normal people do occasionally\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are some things I believe God wants to do in your life and in the life of our church, and what is lacking is not passion, we have passion you have passion\'85but consistency and more importantly consistency in some specific things\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
